FBIS4-39412 "drsov110_b_94022" FBIS-SOV-94-110 Daily Report 7 Jun 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Economic Issues Draft Edict on Foreign Banking Not Pending Draft Edict on Foreign Banking Not Pending MK0706083094 Moscow SEGODNYA in Russian 7 Jun 94 p 1 MK0706083094 Moscow SEGODNYA Russian BFN [Unattributed report: "No Draft Edict on Expanding Foreign Bank Activity Is Pending"] [Text] No draft presidential edict expanding foreign bank activity on Russia territory is being prepared, Sergey Filatov, Russian Federation presidential chief of staff, said yesterday. According to him, "an edict streamlining Russia's banking system is currently in the making but this draft does not affect foreign bank activity."
